urn:schema-org:entity_type:dance_group.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A dance group—for example, the Alvin Ailey Dance Theater or Riverdance.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:dance_group.urn:lri:property_type:label: Dance Group

urn:schema-org:entity_type:defence_estab.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A defence establishment, such as an army or navy base.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:defence_estab.urn:lri:property_type:label: Defence Establishment

urn:schema-org:entity_type:emergency_ser.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: An emergency service, such as a fire station or ER.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:emergency_ser.urn:lri:property_type:label: Emergency Service

urn:schema-org:entity_type:enumeration.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: Lists or enumerations—for example, a list of cuisines or music genres, etc.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:enumeration.urn:lri:property_type:label: Enumeration

urn:schema-org:entity_type:event.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: An event happening at a certain time at a certain location.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:event.urn:lri:property_type:label: Event

urn:schema-org:entity_type:geo_coordinat.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: The geographic coordinates of a place or event.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:geo_coordinat.urn:lri:property_type:label: Geo Coordinates

urn:schema-org:entity_type:geo_shape.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: The geographic shape of a place.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:geo_shape.urn:lri:property_type:label: Geo Shape

urn:schema-org:entity_type:government_of.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A government office—for example, an IRS or DMV office.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:government_of.urn:lri:property_type:label: Government Office

urn:schema-org:entity_type:image_gallery.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: Web page type: Image gallery page.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:image_gallery.urn:lri:property_type:label: Image Gallery

urn:schema-org:entity_type:intangible.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A utility class that serves as the umbrella for a number of 'intangible' things such as quantities, structured values, etc.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:intangible.urn:lri:property_type:label: Intangible

urn:schema-org:entity_type:item_availabi.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A list of possible product availablity options.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:item_availabi.urn:lri:property_type:label: Item Availability

urn:schema-org:entity_type:item_list.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A list of items of any sort—for example, Top 10 Movies About Weathermen, or Top 100 Party Songs. Not to be confused with HTML lists, which are often used only for formatting.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:item_list.urn:lri:property_type:label: Item List

urn:schema-org:entity_type:item_page.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A page devoted to a single item, such as a particular product or hotel.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:item_page.urn:lri:property_type:label: Item Page

urn:schema-org:entity_type:job_posting.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A listing that describes a job opening in a certain organization.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:job_posting.urn:lri:property_type:label: Job Posting

urn:schema-org:entity_type:landform.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A landform or physical feature.  Landform elements include mountains, plains, lakes, rivers, seascape and oceanic waterbody interface features such as bays, peninsulas, seas and so forth, including sub-aqueous terrain features such as submersed mountain ranges, volcanoes, and the great ocean basins.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:landform.urn:lri:property_type:label: Landform

urn:schema-org:entity_type:language.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: Natural languages such as Spanish, Tamil, Hindi, English, etc. and programming languages such as Scheme and Lisp.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:language.urn:lri:property_type:label: Language

urn:schema-org:entity_type:legislative_b.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A legislative building—for example, the state capitol.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:legislative_b.urn:lri:property_type:label: Legislative Building

urn:schema-org:entity_type:local_busines.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A particular physical business or branch of an organization. Examples of LocalBusiness include a restaurant, a particular branch of a restaurant chain, a branch of a bank, a medical practice, a club, a bowling alley, etc.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:local_busines.urn:lri:property_type:label: Local Business

urn:schema-org:entity_type:lodging_busin.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A lodging business, such as a motel, hotel, or inn.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:lodging_busin.urn:lri:property_type:label: Lodging Business

urn:schema-org:entity_type:media_object.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: An image, video, or audio object embedded in a web page. Note that a creative work may have many media objects associated with it on the same web page. For example, a page about a single song (MusicRecording) may have a music video (VideoObject), and a high and low bandwidth audio stream (2 AudioObject's).
urn:schema-org:entity_type:media_object.urn:lri:property_type:label: Media Object

urn:schema-org:entity_type:medical_organ.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A medical organization, such as a doctor's office or clinic.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:medical_organ.urn:lri:property_type:label: Medical Organization

urn:schema-org:entity_type:mountain.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A mountain, like Mount Whitney or Mount Everest
urn:schema-org:entity_type:mountain.urn:lri:property_type:label: Mountain

urn:schema-org:entity_type:music_group.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A musical group, such as a band, an orchestra, or a choir. Can also be a solo musician.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:music_group.urn:lri:property_type:label: Music Group

urn:schema-org:entity_type:music_playlis.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A collection of music tracks in playlist form.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:music_playlis.urn:lri:property_type:label: Music Playlist

urn:schema-org:entity_type:music_recordi.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A music recording (track), usually a single song.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:music_recordi.urn:lri:property_type:label: Music Recording

urn:schema-org:entity_type:offer.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: An offer to sell an item—for example, an offer to sell a product, the DVD of a movie, or tickets to an event.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:offer.urn:lri:property_type:label: Offer

urn:schema-org:entity_type:offer_item_co.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A list of possible conditions for the item for sale.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:offer_item_co.urn:lri:property_type:label: Offer Item Condition

urn:schema-org:entity_type:organization.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: An organization such as a school, NGO, corporation, club, etc.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:organization.urn:lri:property_type:label: Organization

urn:schema-org:entity_type:parking_facil.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A parking lot or other parking facility.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:parking_facil.urn:lri:property_type:label: Parking Facility

urn:schema-org:entity_type:performing_ar.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A theatre or other performing art center.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:performing_ar.urn:lri:property_type:label: Performing Arts Theater

urn:schema-org:entity_type:performing_gr.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A performance group, such as a band, an orchestra, or a circus.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:performing_gr.urn:lri:property_type:label: Performing Group

urn:schema-org:entity_type:person.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A person (alive, dead, undead, or fictional).
urn:schema-org:entity_type:person.urn:lri:property_type:label: Person

urn:schema-org:entity_type:place.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: Entities that have a somewhat fixed, physical extension.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:place.urn:lri:property_type:label: Place

urn:schema-org:entity_type:place_of_wors.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: Place of worship, such as a church, synagogue, or mosque.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:place_of_wors.urn:lri:property_type:label: Place of Worship

urn:schema-org:entity_type:product.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A product is anything that is made available for sale—for example, a pair of shoes, a concert ticket, or a car.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:product.urn:lri:property_type:label: Product

urn:schema-org:entity_type:reservoir.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A reservoir, like the Lake Kariba reservoir.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:reservoir.urn:lri:property_type:label: Reservoir

urn:schema-org:entity_type:residence.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: The place where a person lives.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:residence.urn:lri:property_type:label: Residence

urn:schema-org:entity_type:review.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A review of an item - for example, a restaurant, movie, or store.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:review.urn:lri:property_type:label: Review

urn:schema-org:entity_type:river_body_of.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A river (for example, the broad majestic Shannon).
urn:schema-org:entity_type:river_body_of.urn:lri:property_type:label: River Body of Water

urn:schema-org:entity_type:sea_body_of_w.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A sea (for example, the Caspian sea).
urn:schema-org:entity_type:sea_body_of_w.urn:lri:property_type:label: Sea Body of Water

urn:schema-org:entity_type:search_result.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: Web page type: Search results page.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:search_result.urn:lri:property_type:label: Search Results Page

urn:schema-org:entity_type:site_navigati.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A navigation element of the page.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:site_navigati.urn:lri:property_type:label: Site Navigation Element

urn:schema-org:entity_type:sports_activi.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A sports location, such as a playing field.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:sports_activi.urn:lri:property_type:label: Sports Activity Location

urn:schema-org:entity_type:structured_va.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: Structured values are strings—for example, addresses—that have certain constraints on their structure.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:structured_va.urn:lri:property_type:label: Structured Value

urn:schema-org:entity_type:theater_group.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A theater group or company—for example, the Royal Shakespeare Company or Druid Theatre.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:theater_group.urn:lri:property_type:label: Theater Group

urn:schema-org:entity_type:tvepisode.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: An episode of a TV series or season.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:tvepisode.urn:lri:property_type:label: TV Episode

urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_checkins.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: User interaction: Check-in at a place.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_checkins.urn:lri:property_type:label: User Checkins

urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_comments.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: The UserInteraction event in which a user comments on an item.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_comments.urn:lri:property_type:label: User Comments

urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_download.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: User interaction: Download of an item.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_download.urn:lri:property_type:label: User Downloads

urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_interact.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A user interacting with a page
urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_interact.urn:lri:property_type:label: User Interaction

urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_page_vis.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: User interaction: Visit to a web page.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_page_vis.urn:lri:property_type:label: User Page Visits

urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_plays.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: User interaction: Play count of an item, for example a video or a song.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:user_plays.urn:lri:property_type:label: User Plays

urn:schema-org:entity_type:video_gallery.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: Web page type: Video gallery page.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:video_gallery.urn:lri:property_type:label: Video Gallery

urn:schema-org:entity_type:web_page.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A web page. Every web page is implicitly assumed to be declared to be of type WebPage, so the various properties about that webpage, such as breadcrumb may be used. We recommend explicit declaration if these properties are specified, but if they are found outside of an itemscope, they will be assumed to be about the page
urn:schema-org:entity_type:web_page.urn:lri:property_type:label: Web Page

urn:schema-org:entity_type:web_page_elem.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A web page element, like a table or an image
urn:schema-org:entity_type:web_page_elem.urn:lri:property_type:label: Web Page Element

urn:schema-org:entity_type:wpad_block.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: An advertising section of the page.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:wpad_block.urn:lri:property_type:label: WP Ad Block

urn:schema-org:entity_type:wpfooter.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: The footer section of the page.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:wpfooter.urn:lri:property_type:label: WP Footer

urn:schema-org:entity_type:wpheader.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: The header section of the page.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:wpheader.urn:lri:property_type:label: WP Header

urn:schema-org:entity_type:wpside_bar.urn:lri:property_type:comment_plain: A sidebar section of the page.
urn:schema-org:entity_type:wpside_bar.urn:lri:property_type:label: WP Side Bar
